&gt;&gt;Mahim: Ok, I think I saw a question back
there.

00:29:04.010 --> 00:29:12.990
So the question was where can you go to see
the lovely view where Mandira proposes to

00:29:12.990 --> 00:29:13.990
Rizwan?

